(11, 2, 2, 'MS SQL experience is preferred .NET', '2019-07-31, 22:12', 'Jed', 'dot_net.jpg', '<p style="margin: 0px 0px 6px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1d2129;">Hello Everyone,</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 6px 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1d2129;">I have an exciting opportunity for a Salesforce Software Engineer to work for a world leading company in Poland.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 6px 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1d2129;">This is a 100% remote position however you will need to be based in Poland to apply.</p>\r\n<div class="text_exposed_show" style="display: inline; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1d2129;">\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 6px; font-family: inherit;">Salary: 20k+ zloty per month&nbsp;<br />Type: Preferably Permanent however can consider B2B</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 6px 0px; font-family: inherit;">Please see the details below:<br />You will have worked in a cross functional team of Salesforce Admins and Developers.<br />Experience around internal Salesforce development as well as integrations with external API&rsquo;s.&nbsp;<br />Experienced with the full cycle of a software project; conception, development, deployment, and the continuous improvement stage.<br />Salesforce developer certification is preferred<br />MS SQL experience is preferred<br />.NET experience is preferred</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 6px 0px; font-family: inherit;">If you are interested in this position, please email your updated CV to jmiller@grootandberg.com or call me on +31 207 168 003.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 6px 0px; font-family: inherit;">If you know anyone that might be interested, please can you like/share&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 6px 0px; font-family: inherit;">Thanks everyone and have a great rest of your day/weekend&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>'),
(13, 1, 2, 'Front-end Developerów :', '2019-07-31, 23:08', 'Magdalena', 'js.png', '<div class="_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa" style="white-space: pre-wrap; direction: ltr; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1d2129;"><span class="_4yxo" style="font-weight: 600; color: #4b4f56; font-family: inherit;">Hej Gdańsk! Poszukuję Front-end Developer&oacute;w <span class="_47e3 _5mfr" style="line-height: 0; vertical-align: middle; margin: 0px 1px; font-family: inherit;" title="Emotikon smile"><span class="_7oe" style="display: inline; font-size: 0px; width: 0px; font-family: inherit;" aria-hidden="true">:</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div class="_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa" style="white-space: pre-wrap; direction: ltr; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1d2129;"><span class="_4yxo" style="font-weight: 600; color: #4b4f56; font-family: inherit;">Wynagrodzenie:</span> 13,0 tys. 23,0 tys. brutto na UoP.</div>\r\n<div class="_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa" style="white-space: pre-wrap; direction: ltr; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1d2129;"><span class="_4yxo" style="font-weight: 600; color: #4b4f56; font-family: inherit;">Wymagania:</span> JavaScript, Angular, React, CSS, angielski b2+.</div>\r\n<div class="_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa" style="white-space: pre-wrap; direction: ltr; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1d2129;"><span class="_4yxo" style="font-weight: 600; color: #4b4f56; font-family: inherit;">Narzędzia:</span> Jira, Confluence, GIT, Jenkins, Agile, Scrum, Kanban.</div>\r\n<div class="_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa" style="white-space: pre-wrap; direction: ltr; margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1d2129;">&ldquo;Jako deweloperzy mamy wpływ na to jakie projekty robimy - nie są narzucone z g&oacute;ry. Jeśli zaczniemy wsp&oacute;łpracę z klientem i okaże się że projekt jest słaby