(14, 1, 3, 'Lead React Developer', '2019-07-31, 23:10', 'Weronika', '3302095_0.jpg', '<div style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1d2129;">\r\n<div class="_l53" style="font-weight: bold; overflow: hidden; padding-bottom: 2px; text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;">Lead React Developer</span></div>\r\n<div class="_l56" style="margin-bottom: 9px; font-family: inherit;">\r\n<div class="_l58" style="color: #90949c; font-family: inherit;">Krzyki, Wroclaw, Poland</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="js_7lm" class="_5pbx userContent _3576" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 6px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1d2129;" data-testid="post_message" data-ft="{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;K&quot;}">\r\n<div id="id_5d4203947f43a6c09191773" class="text_exposed_root text_exposed" style="display: inline; font-family: inherit;">\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 6px; font-family: inherit;">Cześć! <span class="_47e3 _5mfr" style="line-height: 0; vertical-align: middle; margin: 0px 1px; font-family: inherit;" title="Emotikon smile"><span class="_7oe" style="display: inline; font-size: 0px; width: 0px; font-family: inherit;" aria-hidden="true">:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 6px 0px; font-family: inherit;">Do software house''u z Katowic poszukujemy Lead React Developera kt&oacute;ry wesprze zesp&oacute;ł zapewniając mentoring i dzielenie się wiedzą</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 6px 0px; font-family: inherit;">Czym się zajmiesz?</p>\r\n<div class="text_exposed_show" style="display: inline; font-family: inherit;">\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 6px; font-family: inherit;">- Rozwojem SPA (React.js, Redux) z Responsive Web Design</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 6px 0px; font-family: inherit;">- Tworzeniem komponent&oacute;w w oparciu o Google Material Design</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 6px 0px; font-family: inherit;">- Ścisłą wsp&oacute;łpracą z programistami (.NET Core, Web API )</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 6px 0px; font-famil